@canyoncoffee..

7 YEARS! // Seven years (and a couple days) ago, Canyon Coffee began with an inaugural pop-up at a friend’s boutique shop in Venice. From the moment we first served our coffee that day, we felt an organic response to Canyon that motivated us to keep going, continue sharing our passion and growing our business. We’ve come a long way since then — we now have a team of 26 amazing people who roast and pack coffee, ship and deliver, provide amazing customer service and support, train and support hundreds of businesses that serve Canyon, and serve up amazing drinks and food at our shop in Echo Park. // It brings us so much joy to still be building Canyon… to have our coffee, playlists, and journals enjoyed by folks around the world; to have opened the doors to the shop and feel the amazing response and community around it; to be on the cusp of opening our new roasting facility here in LA; to be looking at the years ahead with as much excitement as we felt at the beginning, all those years ago. // To celebrate (!!) take 20% on all coffee on canyoncoffee.co today through Sunday :)
